---

## Created Files

| File | Description |
|---|---|
| `infra/main.bicep` | Main Bicep orchestration template — declares all modules and their connections |
| `infra/main.parameters.json` | Default parameter values (environmentName, location, postgresAdminUser, postgresDatabaseName) |
| `infra/modules/managedIdentity.bicep` | User-Assigned Managed Identity for ACR pull and DefaultAzureCredential |
| `infra/modules/logAnalytics.bicep` | Log Analytics Workspace linked to Container App Environment |
| `infra/modules/containerRegistry.bicep` | Azure Container Registry (Basic SKU) + AcrPull role assignment for the MI |
| `infra/modules/postgresql.bicep` | PostgreSQL Flexible Server v17 (Burstable B2s) with AAD auth + Azure Services firewall rule |
| `infra/modules/containerAppEnvironment.bicep` | Container App Environment connected to Log Analytics |
| `infra/modules/containerApp.bicep` | Container App with external HTTPS ingress (port 8080), CORS, user-assigned MI, and DB env vars |
| `infra/deploy.ps1` | Windows PowerShell deployment script (provision + image build via `az acr build` + Service Connector) |
| `infra/deploy.sh` | Linux/macOS Bash deployment script (same steps) |
| `infra/README.md` | Infrastructure documentation with architecture diagram and usage guide |
| `infra/compliance.md` | Line-by-line IaC rules compliance report |

