## Service Connector Configuration

The `az containerapp connection create postgres-flexible` command automatically injected these Spring Boot environment variables:

| Variable | Value |
|---|---|
| `spring.datasource.url` | `jdbc:postgresql://azpg5temr6kkrdrve.postgres.database.azure.com:5432/photoalbum?sslmode=require` |
| `spring.datasource.username` | `aad_photoalbum_pg_connection` |
| `spring.datasource.azure.passwordless-enabled` | `true` |
| `spring.cloud.azure.credential.client-id` | `fedba2f7-2589-47c8-8557-3ab18672e163` |
| `spring.cloud.azure.credential.managed-identity-enabled` | `true` |

